casebody.data:
Warren Rosevelt, Respondent v. Alexander McGaw, Appellant. Decided November 10, 1891. Appeal by defendant from order of reference. Leavitt & Keith, for appellant. William G. Bussey, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., Freedman and Dugro, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Order affirmed, with $10 costs.
